<TEXT>
<P>
KUWAIT CITY, April 12 (Xinhua) -- An official in Kuwaiti
Educational Ministry today hoped the shooting incident Wednesday
in which an Egyptian teacher was shot and seriously injured by a
student would not affect bilateral relations.
</P>
<P>
Kuwaiti Education Undersecretary Mesaeid Al-Haroun, while
expressing denunciation and sorrow over the incident, underlined
that the historic relations with Egypt could never be affected by
