<HEADLINE> Water Treatment To Purify Famous Summer Resort </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHIJIAZHUANG, April 12 (Xinhua) -- Beidaihe, a famous summer
resort in the northern Hebei province, will receive urgent
provincial protection to keep up with the water quality standard
for a vacationland.
</P>
<P>
Water treatment plants will be on the way for a cleaner inflow
into the sea area in Beidaihe, while all the hospitals and
pollutants-heavy enterprises in the region are ordered by the
provincial government to take immediate moves to purify their
drainage.
</P>
<P>
The provincial environment protection administrations will also
keep a closer eye on those pollutants-producers to spare the
Beidaihe of more foul water and purify the sea area before the
summer holiday season.
</P>
<P>
Bordered on the northern Bohai Sea, Beidaihe is a renowned
tourism attraction, summer resort and also an important natural
reserve for birds. 
</P>
