<HEADLINE> Explosive Devices Removed From Pope Route </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SARAJEVO, April 12 (Xinhua) -- Sarajevo's police have
discovered and removed four explosive devices along the route that
Pope John Paul II will take, said local press reports today.
</P>
