He said that "this is an opportunity for serious promotion of
Kenyan tourism in the Gulf states whose residents are wealthy
enough to visit the country's beaches and parks."
</P>
<P>
At the same time, Kombo noted, a number of Kenyan women will
be exhibiting Kenya's crafts and wares during the Gulf event.
</P>
<P>
Arrangements have been made to set up joint programs with the
Middle East-based Arab Woman's Club of Sharjah to improve
commercial ties between women in Kenya and the Gulf region.
</P>
