its colleagues for his negligence Friday. A settlement has been
reached through dialogue between the Airport Authority of India
and the ATC today.
</P>
<P>
Hundreds of passengers were stranded at the Hyderabad Airport
in southern India as flights in both domestic and international
sectors remained suspended for the second day today in view of the
flash strike by the ATC, reports reaching here said.
</P>
<P>
Both the domestic and international airports in the capital of
New Delhi in the past two days have been severely hit by the
strike with many passengers stranded at the airports.  
